1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:01,870
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:01,870 --> 00:00:03,410
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,410 --> 00:00:04,980
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:07,410 --> 00:00:11,620
So you did steal the video
Gong Nan Sook had.

5
00:00:13,820 --> 00:00:16,390
Gong Nan Sook's fate
is in my hands now,

6
00:00:16,390 --> 00:00:18,390
and you,
kind and fragile Joo Ha Neul,

7
00:00:18,820 --> 00:00:22,060
are going to release this video
to the world?

8
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:28,730
It'll be released simultaneously
to newspapers and on social media.

9
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,900
The fact that you, Jin Tae Seok,
are a monster.

10
00:00:37,540 --> 00:00:38,680
Joo Ha Neul.

11
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:41,450
No, you're the one
who's going to die by my hand.

12
00:01:02,730 --> 00:01:06,570
If this were a physical fight,
I'd kill you and not break a sweat.

13
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:09,540
I'm done with your insanity,
Jin Tae Seok.

14
00:01:21,050 --> 00:01:23,150
Mom, what are we going to do?

15
00:01:24,190 --> 00:01:27,360
Dad just tried to kill Ha Neul.

16
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:31,200
Is Dad really a murderer?

17
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:38,500
My poor Se Mi.

18
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:41,410
You always thought
your father was your rock.

19
00:01:43,010 --> 00:01:44,010
Se Mi.

20
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:49,580
You need to know, Se Mi.
The truth about your father.

21
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:52,480
How could he do something like that?

22
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:55,990
I told myself it was all lies
and just made-up stories,

23
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:59,590
and that I must have been seeing things.

24
00:02:00,090 --> 00:02:01,260
Se Mi.

25
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:04,330
Mom, how can I go on living?

26
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:07,570
I'm so scared of Dad.

27
00:02:08,130 --> 00:02:09,130
Se Mi.

28
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,700
Se Mi.

29
00:02:10,970 --> 00:02:13,940
Hey, look at me. Snap out of it.

30
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,270
Look right at me.

31
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:17,780
Just breathe.

32
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,140
Okay.

33
00:02:19,610 --> 00:02:20,610
Se Mi.

34
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,810
I will...

35
00:02:23,380 --> 00:02:26,780
protect you and Jung Won.

36
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:28,890
I'll protect
our whole Kunhyang Family.

37
00:02:29,650 --> 00:02:32,260
But when you're
in front of your father,

38
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,930
don't let on that you know anything.
Okay?

39
00:02:35,330 --> 00:02:37,430
Act as you've always had. Got it?

40
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:45,400
What do you think you can do
with just that pathetic video?

41
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,670
You want to take everyone
down with you?

42
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:52,040
The fact that Gong Nan Sook
killed Se Hoon's birth mother.

43
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:54,380
I'll expose that to the world.

44
00:02:54,380 --> 00:02:56,250
You were the one behind that,
Jin Tae Seok!

45
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,680
And who's going to prove that?

46
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:00,720
Gong Nan Sook will face
a murder charge,

47
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:02,720
so I'll have to cut her loose.

48
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,660
But you'd never.

49
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:06,660
Why?

50
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,330
Because you have people to protect.

51
00:03:09,530 --> 00:03:11,630
Cha Jung Won, Gong Nan Sook.

52
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:15,700
Then I should never forgive you
if I'm to protect them.

53
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:18,100
I will rip you out by the roots.

54
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,340
You're the source of all this evil.

55
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,180
I'll release the video in 24 hours.

56
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:26,880
Consider this your last chance,
Jin Tae Seok.

57
00:03:28,450 --> 00:03:30,380
For the sake of everyone
you've hurt,

58
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,720
this is one last act of mercy.

59
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,540
Just answer my question!

60
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:51,770
Young Chae.

61
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,540
The pregnancy and miscarriage...

62
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:57,480
- Were they all lies?
- What are you talking about?

63
00:03:58,010 --> 00:04:00,950
You’re hurting the feelings of
our sweet A Reum, who passed away.

64
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:08,890
Joo Young Chae.

65
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:11,520
How could she do
something like that?

66
00:04:28,410 --> 00:04:29,910
Se Hoon can't find out.

67
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:31,610
Mom's in a crisis,

68
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:33,040
and if the fake pregnancy
is revealed,

69
00:04:33,610 --> 00:04:35,380
I'll be thrown out
of the Kunhyang family.

70
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:52,730
Why is everything such a mess?
Why can't you stay out of trouble?

71
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:55,030
Ms. Young Chae,
get a hold of yourself.

72
00:04:57,470 --> 00:05:01,840
What's going on?
You have to tell me what's going on.

73
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:09,310
Does Se Hoon suspect something?

74
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:12,080
What do I do?

75
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,050
What do you want to do?

76
00:05:14,790 --> 00:05:15,790
Me?

77
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:19,360
Just do what you want.

78
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:20,660
Do what?

79
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:23,530
Young Chae, what was your goal?

80
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:25,600
To stop being
Chairman Gong's little puppet...

81
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,970
and to see Cha Jung Won ruined.

82
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:31,700
Exactly. So do what you have to do
to see that happen.

83
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,110
Se Mi.

84
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:47,120
- You must've been so shocked.
- Are you okay, Ha Neul?

85
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:49,950
Why would my dad do that to you...

86
00:05:51,890 --> 00:05:53,190
I'm so sorry.

87
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:56,560
Hey, don't apologize.
It's not your fault.

88
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,460
Ha Neul,

89
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,630
I need to know...

90
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:04,000
why all this is happening,
and why my dad...

91
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:06,540
is doing all of this
to you and Jung Won.

92
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:09,040
I'd rather you didn't know.

93
00:06:09,810 --> 00:06:12,240
- It's a lot to handle.
- What am I, a stranger?

94
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,280
Am I a fool?

95
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:16,580
It's about my mom, dad, and sister.
How can I pretend I don't know?

96
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,920
(Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

97
00:06:22,490 --> 00:06:24,660
She deserves to know, Ha Neul.

98
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,290
Jung Won, please tell me.

99
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:29,990
Tell me why Dad did it,
and why he won't stop.

100
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:33,130
Didn't Chairman Han
tell you anything?

101
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,200
She only confirmed my dad did it.

102
00:06:35,530 --> 00:06:37,740
But she refuses to tell me why.

103
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,910
She probably couldn't
bring herself to tell you...

104
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:44,080
because he's not the father
you thought you knew.

105
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,180
Tell me.

106
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,310
About the father I don't know.

107
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:12,900
My dad really did all of that?

108
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:16,440
The one who killed Joo Ha Neul's father,
Joo Sang Cheol,

109
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:20,410
and the one who killed my father
on the stairs at the gallery.

110
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,710
It was all Jin Tae Seok.

111
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,180
Why?

112
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,650
Why would Dad do that?

113
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:27,850
To take Han Hye Ra,

114
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:30,050
my mother, from my father...

115
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,820
and to possess her forever.

116
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,960
He became a monster,
believing that only by killing...

117
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:38,530
could he become stronger
and protect what was his.

118
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,400
- That's Jin Tae Seok.
- No.

119
00:07:41,730 --> 00:07:44,970
No, that's not true.
Dad would never do that.

120
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,240
You'll have to see it for yourself
to believe it.

121
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:26,580
(Dad)

122
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,720
The person you called
is unavailable.

123
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:34,650
- You'll be transferred...
- She's ignoring my calls.

124
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:36,520
Then again,

125
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,390
I guess the director
of the Design Team is just too busy.

126
00:08:43,190 --> 00:08:44,730
What's with that look?

127
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:47,600
- Would you like some tea?
- No.

128
00:08:48,170 --> 00:08:51,270
- What time is it?
- It's 2:20 p.m.

129
00:08:56,170 --> 00:08:58,880
I'll release the video in 24 hours.

130
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:01,210
Consider this your last chance,
Jin Tae Seok.

131
00:09:01,610 --> 00:09:03,580
So, 10 p.m. tonight.

132
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:14,930
I'm sorry.
I haven't been feeling well.

133
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:16,060
Are you feeling unwell?

134
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,460
Well, this isn't a hospital,

135
00:09:19,530 --> 00:09:23,200
so I don't think I should share
the details of my conditions.

136
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:27,470
Word must have reached
your superiors by now.

137
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:29,270
Haven't they told you anything?

138
00:09:29,340 --> 00:09:32,080
The CEO of MO Consulting
was summoned this morning,

139
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,380
and he testified.

140
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:35,980
He said he was just a figurehead,
acting on your orders.

141
00:09:36,050 --> 00:09:37,210
What?

142
00:09:37,210 --> 00:09:39,450
They must be out of their minds!

143
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:45,390
No! I didn't mean you, Prosecutor.
I meant them.

144
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:46,960
We have an accomplice's statement.

145
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:49,890
We confirmed the facts
and a large sum.

146
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:51,930
So...

147
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,370
what's going to happen to me, then?

148
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:07,950
Gong Nan Sook.

149
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,710
You're under arrest
on charges of concealing...

150
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:11,620
and disguising criminal proceeds,
as well as tax evasion.

151
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,450
Wait, hold on.
Did I hear you correctly?

152
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,890
Under arrest?

153
00:10:15,950 --> 00:10:18,660
You have the right to remain silent
and the right to an attorney.

154
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,930
Anything you say can be used
against you in court.

155
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:24,460
- Let's go.
- Wait, stop!

156
00:10:24,730 --> 00:10:27,160
I didn't get to tell my family.

157
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:30,600
My kids will worry.
They're still young, you know.

158
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:32,240
Your family will be notified.

159
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:34,710
No, I told you, my kids are young!

160
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:35,710
Just let me call them.

161
00:10:35,710 --> 00:10:36,710
Prosecutor!

162
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:37,710
I’m not finished talking yet.

163
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:39,540
Hey, wait a second. Let go of me!

164
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:45,720
Should we make it tighter
around the waist?

165
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:49,150
You better not stab me.
I'll stab you right back.

166
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:50,990
Give me a break. Like I'd stab you.

167
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,820
Designer Kim Sung Hee,
you do it, then.

168
00:10:54,330 --> 00:10:55,330
Okay.

169
00:10:57,730 --> 00:11:01,670
By the way, why did Director Jin
suddenly take the afternoon off?

170
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,970
Is something going on at home?

171
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:05,700
She must be embarrassed about
tearing up someone else's design.

172
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:08,510
I'd appreciate it if you didn't talk
about her behind her back.

173
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,470
Especially when it's family.

174
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:12,980
Look at you feeling all sisterly
all of a sudden.

175
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:16,710
You're so protective of your work,
but so forgiving with Director Jin.

176
00:11:17,650 --> 00:11:20,180
Joo Young Chae, I know it was you,
so just shut up.

177
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,350
I'm reaching my limit.

178
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:27,290
Hey, this design turned out great.

179
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:31,630
How about we do a special reveal
for this new collection?

180
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:34,130
- How so?
- How about...

181
00:11:34,130 --> 00:11:37,130
a sneak peek fashion show
in the lobby?

182
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,970
That's a great idea.

183
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,140
I agree.

184
00:11:42,540 --> 00:11:46,640
We can show the team's hard work
and throw an event for the staff.

185
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:52,050
Joo Young Chae,
you should be the main model.

186
00:11:52,450 --> 00:11:55,390
The designer can walk in her show,

187
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:57,320
just like at New York Fashion Week.

188
00:11:59,490 --> 00:12:00,690
Me? On the runway?

189
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:10,270
Joo Young Chae is so shameless,

190
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,540
even after stealing
someone else's design.

191
00:12:11,940 --> 00:12:15,740
No wonder. It looked exactly like
your style, Jung Won.

192
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:17,070
We have to end this now, right?

193
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:19,180
Do you have a plan?

194
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:28,690
I have a bombshell in here.

195
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:32,520
- A bombshell?
- Let's wait for the right moment.

196
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:36,090
Let's make the day
of the fashion show our D-Day.

197
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,600
(Kunhyang Group)

198
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:43,000
You told Se Mi everything?

199
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:44,300
Yes.

200
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,870
It's time Se Mi...

201
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:48,340
knew the truth about
who Jin Tae Seok really is.

202
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:52,240
Poor Se Mi. She must be so hurt.

203
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,950
I just couldn't bring myself...

204
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:58,120
to tell her the whole story.

205
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:00,820
So you didn't tell her...

206
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:03,790
that we're planning revenge
on Jin Tae Seok?

207
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:07,990
Se Mi needs to know
that the family...

208
00:13:07,990 --> 00:13:09,790
she trusted the most
is falling apart.

209
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,660
You're right.

210
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:13,400
If Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok...

211
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,000
finds out that Se Mi knows,

212
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:18,070
what do you think will happen?

213
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,700
For Jin Tae Seok,

214
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:24,070
it'll be a wound
that will never heal.

215
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:33,280
He'll become
the most wounded monster in the world.

216
00:13:35,490 --> 00:13:37,190
A monster who tried to kill...

217
00:13:38,060 --> 00:13:39,560
his biological daughter.

218
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:43,160
So you think he feels fatherly love,
but only for Se Mi?

219
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,830
It's the last grain of sand...

220
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:48,330
of a father's love
left in a murderer.

221
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,970
He’s especially cold
to Se Hoon, though.

222
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:53,800
He groomed him to be his successor.

223
00:13:55,370 --> 00:13:57,810
Just like he tended to me
like a hothouse flower,

224
00:13:58,510 --> 00:13:59,940
he taught him to be stronger...

225
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,980
and to crush others
before they ever crushed him.

226
00:14:03,810 --> 00:14:07,450
- And you call that a father's love?
- It might be his twisted way.

227
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:14,630
Tonight at 10 p.m.

228
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:17,600
You're still sending
the video, right?

229
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:19,830
Yes.

230
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:22,170
But Jin Tae Seok
threatened me again.

231
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:26,900
If I release the video,
he'll tell the world...

232
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:30,310
that Chairman Gong Nan Sook killed
Jin Se Hoon's birth mother.

233
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:33,010
Chairman Gong may have done it,
but the one behind it all...

234
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:35,180
was Jin Tae Seok.

235
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:37,550
So he's just going to cut her loose.

236
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,080
This is about your mother, Ha Neul.

237
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:41,320
This isn't an easy decision.

238
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,320
No,

239
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:44,590
if we stop here again,

240
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,960
we'll never be able to
stop Jin Tae Seok.

241
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:56,770
I'm here to report that
after Chairman Gong Nan Sook...

242
00:14:57,170 --> 00:15:00,040
was brought in by prosecutors
for re-questioning as a suspect...

243
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:13,680
I can't believe it.

244
00:15:14,350 --> 00:15:17,960
To think the invincible Chairman Gong
is in a holding cell.

245
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:23,090
Grandma says for a witch like her,
a jail cell is her second home.

246
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:26,560
If I could,
I'd gladly take her place.

247
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:28,730
Is that true?

248
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:31,900
Someone from the Seoul Prosecutor's Office
called and spouted nonsense.

249
00:15:31,970 --> 00:15:34,070
I figured it was a scam and hung up.

250
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,440
You're telling me it was for real?

251
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:38,780
- She didn't even call me.
- I didn't get a call either.

252
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:42,750
You don't need a call, Chef Hong.
Grandma tells you everything.

253
00:15:43,010 --> 00:15:44,880
What am I supposed to do now?

254
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:50,150
Ask your all-powerful grandma
when my mom is getting out.

255
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:53,390
- She says she won't show for you.
- Why is she playing favorites?

256
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:55,530
What if I call for her?

257
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:58,200
Grandma. Knock, knock.

258
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:03,070
If the world's most beautiful
vixen's guard dog calls,

259
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:05,600
she says she'll make an appearance
for a moment.

260
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:11,980
She says that Gong Nan Sook's fate
depends on her children.

261
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:16,050
It's a lost cause.

262
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:20,850
Hey, I'm her only child.

263
00:16:21,190 --> 00:16:23,590
So is my mom just going to rot
in jail forever, then?

264
00:16:26,990 --> 00:16:29,260
There's still no reaction
from Chairman Jin Tae Seok.

265
00:16:31,930 --> 00:16:33,660
What about
the Kunhyang Association members?

266
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:34,900
No word from them?

267
00:16:34,970 --> 00:16:36,700
I've tried calling several of them,

268
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:40,200
but they're all saying
she's getting what she deserves.

269
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:44,980
She threw money around,
so how does she not have one ally?

270
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:48,450
If we do nothing,
she'll go to a detention center.

271
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:52,620
- And after that...
- After her trial and sentencing,

272
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,750
she'll go to prison.

273
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:56,650
(Kunhyang Group)

274
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:14,970
Why are you ignoring me?

275
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:18,310
You've been acting like
I don't exist all day.

276
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,340
Are you trying to drive me crazy?

277
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,150
You really don't know why?

278
00:17:23,050 --> 00:17:24,680
Is it because my family is
about to be ruined?

279
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,520
So you can't stand me now, too?

280
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:30,120
Young Chae, stop with the lies!

281
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:33,190
- What?
- I heard everything.

282
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:37,490
Don't tell me he found out.

283
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:38,960
What are you talking about?

284
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:41,570
What could be more important
than you going bankrupt?

285
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:43,300
The fake pregnancy
and miscarriage...

286
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,300
Walls have ears, you foolish girl.

287
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:54,950
- I think you're mistaken.
- Just stop it!

288
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:59,080
How could you use A Reum?

289
00:18:00,650 --> 00:18:02,820
I grew attached to A Reum
without even realizing it.

290
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:05,790
I really thought she was
going to be born soon.

291
00:18:11,430 --> 00:18:13,000
I was so wrong.

292
00:18:14,130 --> 00:18:16,170
I lied because I was
afraid of losing you.

293
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:20,470
My mom may have started it,
but I couldn't stop.

294
00:18:22,970 --> 00:18:24,410
That doesn't justify what you did.

295
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:28,210
Having A Reum was the only way
I could have you.

296
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:29,750
What?

297
00:18:30,180 --> 00:18:33,980
When I saw Cha Jung Won take my name
and my place, living with you,

298
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:36,690
I realized what I needed to have.

299
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:40,560
- It was you, Jin Se Hoon.
- I understand that feeling.

300
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:44,090
But you deceived me completely.

301
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:46,660
I loved that you were slowly opening
your heart to me,

302
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:49,630
thinking that I was
actually carrying A Reum,

303
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,900
and I was so grateful.

304
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,840
Young Chae, you're a lot like me.

305
00:18:56,170 --> 00:18:58,680
We had everything
before we even knew we wanted it,

306
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:01,080
and we thought we were
entitled to enjoy it all.

307
00:19:01,150 --> 00:19:03,410
That's why I can't stand
having what's mine taken from me.

308
00:19:04,150 --> 00:19:05,150
Not one bit.

309
00:19:07,990 --> 00:19:09,590
Just don't leave me.

310
00:19:10,450 --> 00:19:13,720
I'm begging you.
I'll do whatever you want.

311
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:15,930
I'll never lie again.

312
00:19:15,990 --> 00:19:17,290
As your wife,

313
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:20,400
I'll do anything to help you climb
as high as you possibly can.

314
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:23,430
Please, just don't leave me...

315
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:25,040
I need time to think.

316
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,770
Go stay at your mother’s
for a while.

317
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:49,060
Se Mi, are you not feeling well?

318
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:50,760
Do you have a fever?

319
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:53,830
I'm fine.

320
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:58,600
I have so much to do
for the fashion show.

321
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,000
I have to get back to work.

322
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:15,020
Something's off with Se Mi.
She's not herself.

323
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:18,660
She's probably just tired
from all the work.

324
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:21,760
No, I think it's something
more than that.

325
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:25,860
Is she still not over Joo Ha Neul?

326
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:28,670
Is she mad at me
for not helping her?

327
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:32,900
Should I do something now?

328
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:34,340
Just stop it.

329
00:20:34,970 --> 00:20:37,310
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul
isn't an object you can acquire.

330
00:20:37,610 --> 00:20:41,280
- You just dote on Se Mi.
- She's my flesh and blood.

331
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:42,580
Then what about Se Hoon?

332
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:47,650
Even if you were raising him
to be your successor,

333
00:20:48,190 --> 00:20:50,190
you were too cold toward him.

334
00:20:50,490 --> 00:20:54,730
It's different with a daughter.
A son needs to be raised tough.

335
00:20:56,730 --> 00:20:58,730
Is that really the only reason?

336
00:20:59,430 --> 00:21:02,370
Fathers always have a soft spot
for their daughters.

337
00:21:03,170 --> 00:21:05,440
What should I do
to make Se Mi feel better?

338
00:21:05,870 --> 00:21:07,740
What if Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul...

339
00:21:08,570 --> 00:21:09,840
leaks that video?

340
00:21:09,910 --> 00:21:11,340
Aren't you even worried about that?

341
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,350
Hye Ra,

342
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:19,320
are you helping Joo Ha Neul?

343
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:23,390
Why would I help Joo Ha Neul?
I'd expose you myself...

344
00:21:24,150 --> 00:21:25,720
if I had that video
in my possession.

345
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:30,660
We’re back to talking like that,
even though we’ve made up.

346
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:31,800
Let's focus on that.

347
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:38,670
I think
you both should come out here.

348
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:45,710
Se Hoon, if you leave me now,
I have nowhere to go.

349
00:21:45,810 --> 00:21:47,280
You can just stay
at your mom's house.

350
00:21:48,610 --> 00:21:49,950
I'll call you
when I've sorted things out.

351
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:53,450
But Chairman Gong Nan Sook
is in a holding cell right now.

352
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:59,260
No one will welcome me if I go back,
so what am I supposed to do?

353
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:05,000
What's going on?

354
00:22:05,430 --> 00:22:07,930
Mother, please,
you have to stop Se Hoon.

355
00:22:08,530 --> 00:22:11,900
Se Hoon, did you just throw
Young Chae out?

356
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:15,070
I just need some time to think.

357
00:22:15,870 --> 00:22:16,870
Time for what?

358
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:19,240
You don't need to know.

359
00:22:24,650 --> 00:22:25,750
Please forgive me.

360
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:29,720
The pregnancy was a lie.
So was the miscarriage.

361
00:22:33,660 --> 00:22:35,430
How could you do such a thing?

362
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:38,330
Young Chae,
are you mocking our family too?

363
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:41,260
I just didn't want to lose Se Hoon.

364
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:43,600
Get out right now!
You will not be my daughter-in-law.

365
00:22:43,770 --> 00:22:46,500
Father,
I'm already part of this family.

366
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:50,870
I'll even overlook the fact that
you had my mother's taxes audited.

367
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,580
Please, just let me stay.

368
00:22:58,550 --> 00:23:01,590
Your mother is in a holding cell,
and you're not even worried?

369
00:23:07,290 --> 00:23:08,390
Does giving birth to me
make her a mother?

370
00:23:09,530 --> 00:23:12,660
I resent Chairman Gong Nan Sook.
I curse her.

371
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:18,140
It's all my mother's fault
that I turned out this way.

372
00:23:57,410 --> 00:23:58,840
Ha Neul.

373
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:02,180
- You'll get hurt. Be careful.
- Mom.

374
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,510
Come here.

375
00:24:04,050 --> 00:24:05,520
My sweet boy.

376
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:26,870
Look at you, all fancy.

377
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:30,870
- Is that real mink?
- Yes. And it was expensive.

378
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:33,110
Take it off. I want to try it on.

379
00:24:36,180 --> 00:24:39,920
I'm not in the mood.
So don't mess with me.

380
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:45,560
Listen to her.
She's not in the mood.

381
00:24:46,190 --> 00:24:49,430
- Now I want to annoy her more.
- Hey, take it off her.

382
00:24:50,660 --> 00:24:52,030
Stop it! Don't!

383
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:55,470
- Come here.
- Hey! I told you to stop!

384
00:24:55,530 --> 00:24:57,700
- Take it off.
- Hey! Darn it!

385
00:24:58,570 --> 00:24:59,570
Hey, this...

386
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:02,170
Darn it!
I'm still making payments on it!

387
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:06,040
Do you think
you're the only tough ones?

388
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,340
Bring it on!

389
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:08,610
Hey, you! Bring it on!

390
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:12,780
- It's on then.
- Okay.

391
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:15,020
Hey!

392
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:19,720
My fists are itching for a fight!
Come on! Let's go!

393
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:22,230
Wait! Hey, that's cheating!

394
00:25:23,190 --> 00:25:24,660
Come on, don't be like that...

395
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,940
I don't want to go
to Madam Gong's house.

396
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,310
Where am I supposed to go?

397
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:44,980
I'm starving.

398
00:25:58,060 --> 00:26:01,800
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

399
00:26:02,970 --> 00:26:05,500
That little brat.
Looks like she got kicked out.

400
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,000
If she got kicked out,
would she be eating that heartily?

401
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:10,910
That girl's always been
off her rocker.

402
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:14,210
Chairman Gong Nan Sook
has it hard enough as it is,

403
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:18,450
and if Ms. Young Chae comes home
after being kicked out...

404
00:26:19,550 --> 00:26:20,980
What's with the sympathy?

405
00:26:22,950 --> 00:26:24,620
They both deserve
whatever's coming to them.

406
00:26:26,060 --> 00:26:29,390
Part-Timer Hwang,
bring her another plate of meat.

407
00:26:29,930 --> 00:26:31,030
What?

408
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:33,830
We're not killing her with kindness.
So why?

409
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:36,330
No matter how much you hate someone,
you can't let them starve.

410
00:26:36,930 --> 00:26:39,540
I'll let her eat her fill,
and then I'll punish...

411
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,240
that little brat.

412
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:49,480
This is Hwang Jung Guk.

413
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:02,390
Manager Gu,
how did you know I was here?

414
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:05,760
Let's go home.

415
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,530
What home?

416
00:27:07,530 --> 00:27:09,530
Ms. Young Chae,
why are you doing this to me too?

417
00:27:10,570 --> 00:27:11,570
Let's go.

418
00:27:19,410 --> 00:27:22,910
(People's Police, Back to Basics)

419
00:27:46,540 --> 00:27:50,040
(Holding Cell)

420
00:28:30,250 --> 00:28:31,410
What do you want to do?

421
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:34,680
What about you?

422
00:28:36,050 --> 00:28:37,390
It's all up to
Chairman Jin Tae Seok.

423
00:28:38,050 --> 00:28:39,420
He's the only one
who can save Chairman Gong.

424
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,160
She's right.

425
00:28:42,060 --> 00:28:43,860
So what do you want me to do?

426
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:47,130
Do what you think is best,
Vice Chairman Joo.

427
00:28:48,130 --> 00:28:51,100
You can either leak the video,
or use it to give...

428
00:28:51,630 --> 00:28:55,110
Jin Tae Seok what he wants
and save Chairman Gong.

429
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:00,280
Whatever the consequences,

430
00:29:02,410 --> 00:29:03,410
I'll face them with you.

431
00:29:24,430 --> 00:29:26,900
The extra 24 hours I gave you
are up.

432
00:29:29,270 --> 00:29:31,270
I trust you brought the video?

433
00:29:43,250 --> 00:29:44,390
I'll bury the video...

434
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:49,060
so it's not seen ever again.
In return...

435
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,590
In return?

436
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:54,030
Prevent Chairman Gong Nan Sook...

437
00:29:55,970 --> 00:29:57,370
from being arrested.

438
00:30:24,590 --> 00:30:27,530
(A Graceful Liar)

439
00:30:49,750 --> 00:30:53,060
I only needed Madam Gong's power
to take down Jin Tae Seok.

440
00:30:53,060 --> 00:30:55,930
You might have to give up everything
you've worked so hard for.

441
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:58,290
How dare you think
you can throw me in prison?

442
00:30:58,390 --> 00:31:01,260
Tearing you apart limb from limb
wouldn't even begin to satisfy me.

443
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:03,530
I want to clear my dad's name.

444
00:31:03,670 --> 00:31:05,740
If we have a recording,
can we file for a retrial?

445
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:08,640
- To prove he's innocent?
- I'll get Jin Tae Seok to confess.

446
00:31:08,770 --> 00:31:10,570
It's best to let the past
stay buried.

447
00:31:10,870 --> 00:31:13,840
Jin Tae Seok will pay
for his crimes.

448
00:31:13,840 --> 00:31:15,550
We'll make sure of it.

449
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:20,350
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
